com.whirvis.jraknet.discovery

Interface DiscoveryListener

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    BroadcastTest.ServerDiscoveryListener

    public interface DiscoveryListener
    Used to listen for events that occur in the Discovery system. In order to listen for events, one must use the Discovery.addListener(DiscoveryListener) method.
    Since:
    JRakNet v2.11.0
    Author:
    Trent Summerlin
    See Also:
    DiscoveredServer, Identifier
